 {ok}‚ÜêDelete(author name);path;jsonpath;dir;remaining
‚çù Delete a user bot from disk and runtime
 ‚éïIO‚Üê0
 path‚Üê##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author,'/',name,'.apln'
 :If ~‚éïNEXISTS path
     ‚éïSIGNAL‚äÇ('EN' 6)('Message'('Bot not found: ',author,'/',name))
 :EndIf
 jsonpath‚Üê##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author,'/',name,'.json'
 ‚éïNDELETE path
 :If ‚éïNEXISTS jsonpath
     ‚éïNDELETE jsonpath
 :EndIf
 ‚çù Remove from runtime
 :If 0‚âÝ##.‚éïNC'UserBots'
     :If 0‚âÝ##.UserBots.‚éïNC‚äÇauthor
         :If 0‚âÝ(##.UserBots‚çéauthor).‚éïNC‚äÇname
             (##.UserBots‚çéauthor).‚éïEX name
         :EndIf
     :EndIf
 :EndIf
 ‚çù Clean up empty author dir
 dir‚Üê##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author
 remaining‚Üê0 ‚éïNINFO‚çÝ1‚ä¢dir,'/*'
 :If 0=‚â¢remaining
